Package net.marfgamer.jraknet.example.chat.client.frame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatBoxKeyListener
    Listens for presses to the enter button in the chat box, used to signal the client to send a chat message.
    ChatFrame
    The frame used by the ChatClient to visualize it's data.
    ComboBoxServerChannelListener
    Listens for changes in the current selected channel, used to set the client channel.
    ConnectServerListener
    Used to listen for presses to the connect/disconnect button in the frame, used to signal the client to connect/disconnect.
    UpdateUsernameBoxListener
    Used to listen for presses to the update username button in the frame, used to signal the client to update the username.
